When browsing any website, WordLabs identifies keywords. Hover over these keywords to get an instant snapshot of relevant information. This feature operates seamlessly in the background, ensuring optimal performance and no hindrance to your browsing experience.

WordLabs currently supports a handful of interests, with more coming. These interests include American Football, Baseball, Football (soccer), and more...
